question: Mlh-mih lū-sîn lūi ū ke hō-sò͘ ê siâⁿ-lūi, chiàⁿ-mih sī hit ê siâⁿ-lūi ê siâⁿ-lūi tī MW?
Oaⁿ-lâi ūi kàu New York chiu ê só͘-chāi ê só͘-ū tiān-chè-chhiúⁿ ê lóng-chóng lóng-ha̍p châi-tiāⁿ (chāi MW lāi) sī kúi-á?
Tī 'nyiso' ê kòng-tiâⁿ lāi-bīn, ū siáⁿ-mih ê siúⁿ-khuán hō͘-chòe tiāⁿ-tiāⁿ, i ê hō͘-chòe kài-sòan ê ji̍t-kî sī siáⁿ-mih?
Kènn-kó͘ só͘-ū tī 2000 niân í-āu chòe-tiâu ê tiān-le̍k chhiúⁿ, Calculate the average number of years between the 'in service year' and the 'license expiration date'.
Chiu chiah bo-chúi-tiân ê miâ, in bô tī 'nyiso' chhī-tiâⁿ, chi̍t ê lūi-hêng ê cha̍p-lî hong-chúi koh-khah-kóa niá 700 MW?

Tī só͘-liè ê sèng-chè tiān chong-chè thong-chè ê kong-lūi tiong, ū sì-chē hun-chi-tōe sī iōng 'boiling water reactor' ê tiān chong-chè lâi thian-chi-chè? Chòe-chòe ê hun-chi-tōe, chū-chòe 2 ê sió-sò͘-tiám chòe ê sió-sò͘-tiám.
Nāi-su jiā-tsuā ê 'pressurized water' tō-ûn iâⁿ-lâi ū 10% ê cheng-kiâ, 'indian point 3 ( c )' tsiap-tiâⁿ ê sin cûn-chúi tiāⁿ-lē uī-hó?
Chik n̂g-thong chēⁿ lâi siau-kiâⁿ ê sî-chūn kap i ê siū-koân-būi-lāi chioh-chè ê kî-kan (siū-koân kiâⁿ-chhiat nî-tāi chiūⁿ chioh-chè nî-tāi) kā-sǹg. Ū ē-tàng khòaⁿ-chhut ê hong-hiòng bô?
answer: Chhú-sî ê nî-tāi kap siū-koân-būi-lāi ê chioh-chè kî-kan bô chin chē ê koan-liân. Hō͘-sǹg ê kî-kan sī: Pilgrim (chhú-sî 1999) - 60 hō͘, FitzPatrick (2000) - 59 hō͘, Indian Point 3 (2000) - 39 hō͘, Indian Point 2 (2001) - 39 hō͘, Vermont Yankee (2002) - 60 hō͘, kap Palisades (2007) - 60 hō͘. Kàu-taⁿ chiah lâi chhú-sî ê tiān-chhiⁿ (chhin-chhiūⁿ Palisades tī 2007) ū khah tn̂g ê kî-kan (60 hō͘), lâi chhú-sî khah chá ê tiān-chhiⁿ (chhin-chhiūⁿ Indian Point tiān-chhiⁿ tī 2000/2001) mā ū khah té ê kî-kan (39 hō͘). Hō͘-sǹg ê kî-kan hām chhú-sî ê ji̍t-kî bô koan-hē.

question: Guáⁿ-chi̍t ê le̍k-tiûⁿ ū chi̍t-ê chū-liōng-lâi kóng siúⁿ-tiâu ê lêng-liōng-tiûⁿ ê chū-liōng pâi tī lēng-gōa ê chū-liōng ê pâi-miâ chū-liōng chū-liōng chiâⁿ chū-liōng ū chū-liōng pâi chū-liōng pâi

Tī chit ê chu-liāu-khò͘ lāi-bīn, goân-chū `capacity - reactor type` chit ê khò͘ í-gōa, ū nn̄g ê khò͘ ê chu-liāu lāi-bīn ū pâi-tiâu-chhiúⁿ ê tùi-chhaú, che ē-tàng kóng-bêng in khó-lêng liân kàu phó͘-lí bô chāi tī chit ê piâⁿ-á lāi-bīn ê chù-kha ia̍h-sī kái-soeh?
Tī chhùi sî-chūn thiah-koè ê tiān-le̍k-chhiúⁿ sī chéng koá?
